{"url": "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510/http://www.whowhatwear.com:80/breezy-pants", "text": "While we definitely don't envy anyone who has to wear full-length trousers to work all summer long, even on the most oppressively humid days, it's nice to have the option of a breezy pair of pants to throw on instead of a dress once in a while. Especially as cooler August nights set in, wide-leg styles in linen, cotton, and silk are becoming especially appealing, and they look far more elegant than denim cutoffs ever could.\n\nTry wearing Madewell's white culottes to brunch with a silk blouse styled off the shoulders and tied in the front, or opt for an ankle-grazing striped pair with a crisp white tee and simple leather sandals. Because they're so versatile, they're also a great choice to toss in your suitcase for weekend trips and longer holidays alike\u2014and, unlike many dresses (unfortunately), they come equipped with pockets.\n\nBelow, shop 15 easy late-summer pants to wear from now until fall.", "images": ["https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783446979-product.600x0c.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783446979-product.480x480uc.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783446339-product.600x0c.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783451985-product.480x480uc.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783451646-product.480x480uc.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-1501783446339-product.480x480uc.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20170812145510im_/https://cdn.cliqueinc.com/posts/231498/breezy-pants-231498-15